Thanks! Poor girl... She joined the list of great musicians who died at 27. RIP Amy.
Thanks!! Always liked Amys' Music, Always will :( RIP

Farewell Amy, say hello to Jim, Jimi, Janis, Elvis and Michael.
R.I.P
Saw her in the IOW festival in 2007 and she was amazing. She will be sorely missed. RIP Amy x
had to get this after she joined the '27' club

As a recovering addict myself, I know the pull drugs and alcohol have on someone. I'm not saying that's how she died but I was always rooting for her somehow. My condolences to Miss Winehouse's family and loved ones. Godspeed Amy! I pray that you've finally found peace.

RIP Amy. I was supprised when i found out she had been diagnosed with bipolar disorder. Not because it does not fit, but because i had not heard about it until she had died. Where was the help for her! i have bipolar and was forced into hospital for much less. so tragic...
thanks in memory of the artist
